<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="376" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1239,1626]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1347,1373]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Barnard, J. L. &amp; Karaman, G. S." box="[325,631,1347,1374]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="866" refId="ref4490" refString="Barnard, J. L. &amp; Karaman, G. S. (1991) The families and genera of marine gammaridean Amphipoda (except marine gammaroids). Records of the Australian Museum, Supplement 13, 1 D 866. https: // doi. org / 10.3853 / j. 0812 - 7387.13.1991.367" type="journal article" year="1991">Barnard &amp; Karaman, 1991</bibRefCitation>
designated 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barnard &amp; Karaman" authorityYear="1991" box="[769,884,1347,1373]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[769,884,1347,1373]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Plumithoe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on 
<taxonomicName authority="Ledoyer, 1979" authorityName="Ledoyer" authorityYear="1979" box="[1005,1432,1347,1373]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Ampithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumicornis">
<emphasis box="[1005,1255,1347,1373]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Ampithoe plumicornis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer, M." box="[1265,1432,1347,1373]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="137 - 181" refId="ref5103" refString="Ledoyer, M. (1979) Expedition Rumphius II (1975) Crustaces parasites, commensaux, etc. (Th. Monod et R. Serene, ed.) VI. Crustaces Amphipodes Grammariens. Bulletin du Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle, Paris, Series 4, Section A, 1, 137 - 181." type="journal article" year="1979">Ledoyer, 1979</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Poor &amp; Lowry (1991) accepted it as Indo-west Pacific genus and considered having setose articles 3–5 on second antenna as diagnostic character.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1239,1626]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">
The material of Iranian coasts agrees with 
<taxonomicName authority="Myers, 2012" authorityName="Myers" authorityYear="2012" box="[676,1054,1455,1482]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">
<emphasis box="[676,905,1455,1481]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">P. madagascariensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Myers, A. A." box="[912,1054,1455,1482]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="1 - 25" refId="ref5574" refString="Myers, A. A. (2012) Amphipoda (Crustacea) from Palau, Micronesia: Families Ampeliscidae, Ampithoidae, Aoridae, Colomastigidae and Cyproideidae. ZooKeys, 193, 1 - 25. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 193.3109" type="journal article" year="2012">Myers, 2012</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
based on the characters of second male gnathopod and first coxa. 
<bibRefCitation author="Myers, A. A." box="[502,655,1491,1518]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="1 - 25" refId="ref5574" refString="Myers, A. A. (2012) Amphipoda (Crustacea) from Palau, Micronesia: Families Ampeliscidae, Ampithoidae, Aoridae, Colomastigidae and Cyproideidae. ZooKeys, 193, 1 - 25. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 193.3109" type="journal article" year="2012">Myers (2012)</bibRefCitation>
studied 
<collectingCountry box="[749,875,1491,1517]" name="Micronesia" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Micronesia</collectingCountry>
samples and reviewed 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ledoyer" baseAuthorityYear="1978" box="[1135,1347,1491,1517]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutus">
<emphasis box="[1135,1347,1491,1517]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Plumithoe hirsutus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
records that were described as variation of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kunkel" authorityYear="1910" box="[553,737,1527,1553]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Ampithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pollex">
<emphasis box="[553,737,1527,1553]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">Ampithoe pollex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer, M." box="[783,963,1527,1553]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="197 - 332" refId="ref5064" refString="Ledoyer, M. (1978) Amphipodes gammariens (Crustacea) des biotopes cavitaires organogenes recifaux de l'ile Maurice (Ocean Indien). The Mauritius Institute Bulletin, 8 (3), 197 - 332." type="journal article" year="1978">Ledoyer (1978)</bibRefCitation>
. Based on 
<bibRefCitation author="Myers, A. A." box="[1089,1246,1527,1554]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="1 - 25" refId="ref5574" refString="Myers, A. A. (2012) Amphipoda (Crustacea) from Palau, Micronesia: Families Ampeliscidae, Ampithoidae, Aoridae, Colomastigidae and Cyproideidae. ZooKeys, 193, 1 - 25. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 193.3109" type="journal article" year="2012">Myers (2012)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer, M." box="[1260,1436,1527,1553]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="197 - 332" refId="ref5064" refString="Ledoyer, M. (1978) Amphipodes gammariens (Crustacea) des biotopes cavitaires organogenes recifaux de l'ile Maurice (Ocean Indien). The Mauritius Institute Bulletin, 8 (3), 197 - 332." type="journal article" year="1978">Ledoyer (1978)</bibRefCitation>
samples belong to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ledoyer" baseAuthorityYear="1978" box="[361,478,1563,1589]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutus">
<emphasis box="[361,478,1563,1589]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">P. hirsutus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Also he assigned 
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer, M." box="[688,863,1563,1589]" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" pagination="1 - 598" refId="ref5162" refString="Ledoyer, M. (1982) Crustaces amphipodes gammariens. Familles des Acanthonotozomatidae a Gammaridae. Faune de Madagascar, 59 (1), 1 - 598." type="journal article" year="1982">Ledoyer (1982)</bibRefCitation>
records of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ledoyer" baseAuthorityYear="1978" box="[990,1108,1563,1589]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutus">
<emphasis box="[990,1108,1563,1589]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">P. hirsutus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a new species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Myers" authorityYear="2012" class="Malacostraca" family="Ampithoidae" genus="Plumithoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="9" pageNumber="376" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="376">P. madagascariensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
